"description": "<p>For the last four weeks we've covered various topics related to the philosophy of math, abstraction, and information. In this meeting we'll do a retrospective in summary on what we've covered. We'll then try to broaden our view of the topics and see how they relate to other areas of philosophy such as philosophy of science, meta-ethics, epistemology and whatever else we can think of. This will help orient us to new topics in the coming month.</p> ",
